  "body": [
    "Belonging to the rababi lineage, Bhai Jagjit Singh Komal hails from Patiala and is the younger brother of Bhai Bahadur Singh Rocket. He has been in service at Sri Harmandir Sahib, Amritsar as a Hazoori Raagi for many years and has also toured abroad to many countries including the UK and USA. If anyone has more recordings or information about Bhai Jagjit Singh Komal, please contact us.",
    "The following batch of recordings are from Dera Mitha Tiwana, Hoshiarpur on 16th February 2001. Here is a link to their youtube channel for a great collection of recordings https://www.youtube.com/user/sewapanthi"
  ],
